name: Odyssey
description:
Odyssey is an expanded re-work of Ivory. It is a very versatile and competent model.

Semi-realistic anime style with good contrast and bright colors.

Some assets attained from MidJourney enable this model to produce fantastic landscapes/objects as well.

Works well with LORA/textual inversions.

For best results, generate at (512,768) or (768,512) resolutions.

NSFW capable although far from a strictly hentai model.

All sample images generated using Euler A sampling method at 20 steps.

Upscaled using Foolhardy Remacri at 0.3 denoising strength.

Images are not cherry picked to show true performance.
